### Phase 3: Initialization ‚ÄĒ Slot Arrays at Spawn

#### [MODIFY] [SpawnSystem.js](file:///e:/WebGames/Onigiri/src/systems/SpawnSystem.js)

When any unit is created/spawned, initialize its melee slot tracking:

```js
unit.meleeSlots = new Array(unitDef.maxMeleeSlots).fill(null); // null = free, occupantId = taken
unit.claimedSlotIdx = null;   // Which slot index this unit has claimed on its target
unit.slotTargetId = null;     // ID of the target this unit has a slot on
unit.slotTargetX = null;      // Cached world X of the claimed slot
unit.slotTargetY = null;      // Cached world Y of the claimed slot
unit.stance_override = null;  // 'SCREENING' or null
```

