### Phase 4: Visual Feedback (Optional but Recommended)

#### [MODIFY] Renderer (Canvas drawing layer)

Units in `SCREENING` stance are drawn with a **subtle visual indicator** ‚ÄĒ a faint grey shield icon or a 30%-opacity white ring around them ‚ÄĒ so the player can see their army is organized, disciplined, and waiting. This does not change gameplay but dramatically elevates the "God-game" feel.

