## Risk Notes

> [!WARNING]
> **Cavalry Charge:** The `chargeTimer > 0` path in [CombatSystem.js](file:///e:/WebGames/Onigiri/src/systems/CombatSystem.js) applies `shoveDir` to knock targets back. When a cavalry unit is charging, it should **bypass slot claiming** and collide directly (the charge is a special move, not a sustained melee engagement). We will add a `if (unit.chargeTimer > 0) skip slot logic` guard.

> [!NOTE]
> **Ikki Rebel (Suicide Unit):** The Rebel has a special-case early-exit on line 95 of [CombatSystem.js](file:///e:/WebGames/Onigiri/src/systems/CombatSystem.js) (`unit.hp = 0`). This unit should also bypass slot claiming since it dies on first contact. We will add a guard for `unit.name === 'Ikki Rebel'`.
